        <productcategorycomponent product="{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/700CL-X-HERITAGE_Nebula-Black.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;700CL-X HERITAGE&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;Does X mark the unknown, or does it call us to infinite possibilities?\r\nWhen faced with the uncertain, some find an equation to be solved.\r\nOthers find themselves at the threshold of possibility.\r\nThere are no guarantees on the journey ahead, only miles to be enjoyed on the road ahead. Embrace the possibilities, remove the boundaries and dare to explore diverse terrain. Fraught as it may be with challenges along the way, freedom is on the journey.\r\nThe bold will enjoy every moment of twisting the throttle toward tomorrow.&#34;,&#34;specificationImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/700CL-X_银河灰_左侧45.png&#34;,&#34;categoryButton&#34;:&#34;Download brochure&#34;,&#34;imageAreas&#34;:[{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;555,489,27&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;1&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;647,418,32&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;2&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;670,203,34&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;3&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;888,539,27&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;4&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;615,506,23&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;5&#34;}],&#34;imageRealWidth&#34;:1140,&#34;imageRealHeight&#34;:760}" image="assets/images/700CL-X-HERITAGE_Nebula-Black.png" category="{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;700&#34;,&#34;button&#34;:&#34;Find a Distributor&#34;,&#34;link&#34;:&#34;/content/cfmoto/global/about-us/global_distributors&#34;,&#34;tips&#34;:&#34;CFMOTO models may have different specifications to comply with local regulations, and maybe modified to meet specific demands in a particular region.&#34;,&#34;downloadBrochureText&#34;:&#34;Download brochure&#34;,&#34;downloadBrochureLink&#34;:&#34;assets/images/documentation/2020_700CL-X HERITAGE brochure.pdf&#34;,&#34;downloadName&#34;:&#34;2020_700CL-X HERITAGE brochure.pdf&#34;,&#34;motorcycleType&#34;:&#34;MOTORCYCLE&#34;,&#34;pointData&#34;:[{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;ENGINE&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point0&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;Powered by an all-new liquid-cooled 693cc parallel twin engine, the 700CL-X produces up to 55kW, plus 68 Nm of smooth, flowing power. The optimised intake system improves the airflow efficiency for quick-revving power. BOSCH EFIand electronic throttle technology, integrated with high-precision sensors to produce clean,efficient fuel atomisation.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20200728084806.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/01@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;LIGHTWEIGHT&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point1&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The newly designed split frame and aluminium alloy swingarm make the curb weight of 700CL-X Heritage only 196kg, which ensures a high power-to-weight ratio, responsive handling and precise control.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20200728084819.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/02@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;ERGONOMICS&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point2&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;In order to meet the needs of daily riding and off-road travel CFMOTO not only carefully crafted the handling capabilities of the 700CL-X Heritage, but also paid great attention to the ergonomics.The engineers carefully considered the rider triangle for optimum comfort, with the 800mm seat height and upright handlebars to keep your riding experience more relaxed&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20200728084833.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/03@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;SUSPENSION&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point3&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;KYB 41mm USD front forks and a link-mounted KYB single rear shock provide a smooth ride on board the 700CL-X. Dial in your ideal setting for comfort and terrain with single-side adjustability on the front,(preload and compression on the left,and preload and rebound on the right) plus preload and rebound adjustability in the rear shock&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20200728084846.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/04@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;SLIPPER CLUTCH&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point4&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The CF-SC slipper clutch helps provide smooth, effortless clutch control, which also reduces the rear-wheel chatter when downshifting. Put the quick-revving power of the 700CL-X to optimum use, with smoother acceleration and reduced engine braking. The slipper clutch gives you improved handling performance while providing better safety riding experience&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20200728084900.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/05@2x.jpg&#34;}]}" variant="[{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/700CL-X-HERITAGE_Nebula-Black.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Nebula-Black&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/color-icon/Nebula-Black.png&#34;},{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/700CL-X-HERITAGE_Zephyr-Blue.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Zephyr-Blue&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/color-icon/Twilight Blue.png&#34;}]"/>
